headline: Air Canada suspends Cuba flights as island set to run out of jet fuel
summary: By Dave Sherwood and Allison Lampert HAVANA/MONTREAL, Feb 9 (Reuters) - Air Canada said on Monday it is suspending flights to Cuba, which warned it was running out of jet fuel, as the U. tightens its grip on the communist-run nation's oil supply.
